{"tid":1295099,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解有條例叫非法集結?","createTime":"2019-07-08T02:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T02:52:57.000Z","uid":223352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"037e6f1441d1b7d2bbe9b6401ff00bd8dde126d3","tid":1295099,"uid":223352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"《公安條例》第18條，非法集結定義為，(1)：凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起；(2)：作出擾亂秩序的行為或作出帶有威嚇性、侮辱性或挑撥性的行為；(3)：意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，即屬非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n咁香港仲叫唔叫有集會自由?"},{"pid":"03f5b5f76c23a63629252ffb519a7077815b1e82","tid":1295099,"uid":223352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"9c64abc25437d480cc2bc4d777d922a2ffc73e2e","tid":1295099,"uid":274602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:45:46.000Z","msg":"歷史原因係因為67暴動。<br />\n到80-90年代，當時香港政府已經修例，放寬咗《公安條例》好多嘅限制。<br />\n到1995年立法局選舉，彭定康推行改革，增加直選議席。中共唔承認呢個立法局，另起爐灶設立臨時立法會，基本上差唔多全部都係建制派。而當時佢哋就將「非法集結」復活。<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.civicparty.hk/?q=node/7523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.civicparty.hk%2F%3Fq%3Dnode%2F7523&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=1fa79a21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.civicparty.hk/?q=node/7523</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B_(%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B_%28%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%29&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=116e66e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B_(%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF)</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%2587%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=c5534881\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83</a>"},{"pid":"b1ddb0b3c9a350608facfe3723bc55ebf114a5fd","tid":1295099,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"所以話中英賣港聲明係英國佬不負責任，聲明寫明集會自由都冇用，根本冇人去睇法律條文。"}]}